                " MULTIPLIER FOR THE SCATTERED NEUTRONS, THE EFFICIENCY",
                " OF THIS DETECTOR FOR FISSION NEUTRONS IS SMALL,",
                ".PROTON RECOIL DETECTOR (LIQUID SCINTILLATOR",
                " NE 213 WITH 3 CM THICKNESS AND 11 CM DIA. AND XP 1040",
